import React from 'react'; import './Usaa.css'; const Usaa = () => { return (
Client: USAA, San Antonio TX
Oct 31, 2017 to April,2018
Role: UI and Core Java Developer
Sravankumar.tangella@Usaa.com
Tools and Technologies Used:

Tools and Technologies Used: Core Java, JSR, Junit, Control-m

Descriptions:
Project 1 Name: Shared_PQ

USAA call centre receives numerous calls per day, all dialed-in customer information is stored in 3P file format in different locations respectively in referent databases. This application works as a translation layer to process these 3P files saves in different databases. These 3P files reached to the system on a scheduled manner and stores in OADB Databases, Shared PQ JSR Batch gathers this data from different databases and stores in centralized QA Report Database, Share PQ handles the burden in removing the redundant 3p records and reprocessing 3P files in its business defined manner

Responsible:

- High ability to work on agile methodology.
- Played vital role in Application Development.
- Well Versed in writing Core Java Modules.
- Contributed effectively in implementing JSR Batch job.
- Writing junit test cases.
- Playing vital role in writing JSR scripts in xml file .
- Raising service request for crating databases, AWC, RTC components deploy in different environment.
- Creating new component my application RTC Repository.
- Scheduling the control-m Jobs in the specified time.

Project 2 Name: BAT2.0
Tools and Technologies Used: React and Redux, Html, CSS, Flexbox, Mock Plus and Node.Js
Descriptions:

USAA The Bulk Attribute Tool(BAT) is used to alter the attributes of agents both in bulk and individually. An Attribute identify a call routing requirement, such as language, location, or Agent expertise. Here we using Tool React and redux for design and connecting API. We are using React for Design Single pages and Redux we are using for API connecting We are creating our Own components not using the other components

Responsible:

- Design, develop and build application using React and Redux consuming the payloads received from the Java Web API Core 2.0.
- Design the all Wireframes and Sketch as per my Client requirements.
- Explored the concepts of Components, Directives, Services and Routing in React.
- Created front-end unit tests using Mocha for React Action methods and Reducers helped QA create TSQL tests during swarming sessions to meet sprint deadlines.
- Created React components.
- Working with CSS3, JavaScript, React JS and ES6 for developing user interface.
- Implemented content switching using React JS routing and fetched data through asynchronous call.
- Utilized React-Router (v2-4) to provide consistent user-facing routing across the application.
- Using GitLab Repository.

)} export default Usaa;
